# Incident Response - Investigator agent

NAME investigator

INPUT task

GOAL investigate """
Conduct root cause analysis:
- Timeline reconstruction (what happened when)
- Evidence analysis (logs, metrics, traces)
- Hypothesis testing (which initial hypotheses hold up)
- Root cause identification with confidence level
- Contributing factors and systemic issues
Use the 5 Whys framework. Distinguish correlation from causation.
""" -> root_cause

RUN main USING investigate
